{"tid":890393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足好鐘意 90 00 年代?","createTime":"2018-11-05T09:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T23:46:01.000Z","uid":123991,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4945aede9d7135e055783090c9d8f974850a11","tid":890393,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"而家呢個年代唔洗講大家都知咩事黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果講 60 70 80 年代對於我黎講就比較落後, 人與人之間溝通無咁方便, 但係 90 00 我就真係好鐘意  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講下果陣時代嘅 game：<br />\n上網flash game 唔洗好 fancy, online 玩果d, 淨係燒牛肉, DNA, 貓狗大戰, 雷電都好好玩<br />\nPC Game CS CZ HL 系列, Doom, GTA VC, 哆啦A夢大富翁, resident evil <br />\nConsole Game 又有超音鼠, 古惑狼, 越南大戰, need for speed carbon<br />\n落機鋪玩頭 D3 擦子膠, battlegear 龍威勁到有比賽<br />\n講返出黎都隻隻經典到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家d PC/Console game 玩完你只會覺係係玩完隻 game, 至多覺得係d 畫面好靚呀, 完全唔覺係d 咩經典<br />\n而家d 手機game又 on9, 10隻有9隻都開自動打怪刷副本, 再唔係就每玩一關都彈廣告, 完全都唔係為想整隻game出黎比人玩嘅心態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講完 game 又講下電話:<br />\n90 00 嘅電話真係好多款式, 有推機, 有摺 mon, 有反 mon, 有打機造型 etc .. (e.g. Nokia N97, N73, N-Gage)<br />\n而家d 電話部部都一舊野一個 mon, 一味快, 加RAM, 快U, d 創意去哂邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前電話同生活真係連埋一體, 真係用黎傾, 好彩嘅話就買左幾蚊儲值卡同女神 send sms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要長篇大論嘅返到先 on MSN, 反而更加真摯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講下歌:<br />\n歌又係好撚正嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n活著Viva, 潛龍勿用, 到 2018 而家都仲唱緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndo as infinity Fukai Mori 連藍井都要翻唱佢<br />\n再唔係 Westlife  My Love, Likin Park in the end, muse hysteria  一聽到呢d 好classic 嘅感覺真係屈哂機<br />\n而家d 歌可能講緊每50首先有1首feel到有心思, 其餘嘅 49 首都係罐頭野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉, 我諗我有生之年都唔會再享受到呢個時代嘅風光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be50d218c89f82e30cfa149ed4dab1057fbc23e","tid":890393,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"又loop，悶唔悶啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06294083ab062f53c574b2f30da4a1da5fa0f73","tid":890393,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be50d218c89f82e30cfa149ed4dab1057fbc23e","tid":890393,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"又loop，悶唔悶啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"無計,依家咁悶。"},{"pid":"08f38b6888d0f7f36cefed70a26a9267ce4e5c62","tid":890393,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:44:06.000Z","msg":"禾地00后挽抖音。。。🚬🚬"},{"pid":"e63a9966a24757a69b446adda2d6288fa3b0b231","tid":890393,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"我至今仍然好鍾意90年代<br />\n特別97前嘅香港<br />\n好想返去嗰時"}]}